                        </p>
                        
                        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 0;">
                            <span style="background: #e74c3c; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; width: 80%; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                                📧 Email: <strong style="color: #fff;">josue.team@admin.com</strong>
